name: Sobre Objetos Digitales (01)

(01)
"Sobre Objetos Digitales"
.mp4, 674 x 1012px
2022

———

los objetos digitales
obtienen valor

por su distribución
en comunidades

la exclusión y la unicidad
no le dan valor

le da valor
que se distribuya

que sea modificado
mutado

creando diferentes
mundos.

———

digital objects
attain value

from their distribution
within communities

exclusion and uniqueness
don't give them value

they attain value
as they are distributed

as they become modified
mutated

creating different
worlds.

———
